-- Cypriot Cabinet Approves Legislation to Support Banks, CyBC Says
-- B y   S t e l i o s   O r p h a n i d e s
-- 2012-05-17T10:52:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-17/cypriot-cabinet-approves-legislation-to-support-banks-cybc-says.html
Cyprus’s cabinet has approved draft
legislation to support the country’s financial institutions at
an extraordinary meeting today, state radio  CyBC  reported,
without saying how it got the information.  The legislation, which allows the state to underwrite
shares issued to support Cypriot financial institutions, will be
debated in parliament today under a fast-track procedure,
Nicosia-based CyBC said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stelios Orphanides in Nicosia at 
